35:40.179 --> 35:41.221
(TIRES SCREECHING)

35:41.305 --> 35:43.932
Oh, oh, I love you so

35:43.975 --> 35:46.643
Uh, uh, I can't let you go

35:46.686 --> 35:49.521
Ooh, ooh, don't tell me no

35:49.605 --> 35:51.857
I need your love tonight

35:51.941 --> 35:54.568
Oh, gee, the way you kiss

35:54.652 --> 35:57.237
Sweedee, too good to miss

35:57.321 --> 36:00.157
Wowee, I want more of this

36:00.241 --> 36:02.951
I need your love tonight

36:02.994 --> 36:05.328
I've been waiting just for tonight

36:05.413 --> 36:08.123
To do some lovin' and hold you tight

36:08.166 --> 36:10.500
Don't tell me, baby, you gotta go

36:10.585 --> 36:13.503
I got the hi-fi high
and the lights down low

36:13.546 --> 36:16.006
Hey, now, hear what I say

36:16.090 --> 36:18.842
Oh, wow, you better stay

36:18.926 --> 36:21.511
