36:53.669 --> 36:56.046
I need your love tonight

36:56.130 --> 36:58.590
Oh, gee, the way you kiss

36:58.674 --> 37:01.301
Sweedee, too good to miss

37:01.385 --> 37:04.179
Wowee, I want more of this

37:04.222 --> 37:11.811
I need your love tonight

37:11.896 --> 37:14.397
(HUMS I NEED YOUR LOVE TONIGHT)

37:14.482 --> 37:15.899
Oh, yeah.

37:18.110 --> 37:21.947
The great goddess Hi'iaka... That's me.

37:22.240 --> 37:26.117
And the brave mortal Lohi'au...

37:26.410 --> 37:28.828
Whoa. That's also me.

37:29.830 --> 37:30.914
Whoa.

37:33.084 --> 37:34.709
Were best friends.

37:36.087 --> 37:37.295
Lilo, look.

37:37.380 --> 37:41.216
- Their friendship proved...
- I'm good now. No more badness.

37:41.592 --> 37:42.926
Oh, sorry.

37:43.886 --> 37:45.178
(SIGHS)

37:45.596 --> 37:48.306
- The great goddess Hi'iaka...
- Stitch good.

37:48.391 --> 37:50.475
Stitch, just get outta here.

37:50.685 --> 37:51.935
Fuzzball.

37:53.271 --> 37:55.772
- No, you out.
- No, you.

37:55.856 --> 37:58.650
- You. You!
- You. You!

37:58.734 --> 37:59.818
Fine.

38:00.319 --> 38:01.861
I will.

38:02.947 --> 38:05.073
- No, Stitch will.
- I'm leaving first.

38:05.116 --> 38:08.285
- I'm leaving first! I am.
- No! Stitch first!

38:08.452 --> 38:11.621
Who took my hair...
Who took my hair dryer?

38:11.747 --> 38:14.624
Get back here. You'll be sorry.

38:14.959 --> 38:18.211
- Open this door, trog.
- Who's there?

38:18.296 --> 38:20.714
- Stitch. Open the door.
- Okay.

38:21.590 --> 38:23.216
What is up with you two?

38:23.301 --> 38:25.510
- Nani, it's me.
- Neither of you move.

38:25.594 --> 38:26.594
(BOTH GROWL)

38:27.138 --> 38:29.639
Oh, David, I'm glad you're here...

38:29.807 --> 38:31.057
David?

38:31.142 --> 38:34.102
Nani, you're not the only fish in the sea.

38:34.145 --> 38:38.523
- PLEAKLEY: Tell her you have...
- Because I have a lot of... uh...

38:38.607 --> 38:42.319
- Tell her your options.
- Options?

