Ai-ya.

38:58.377 --> 39:01.379
- She's touching me.
- I'm not touching you.

39:01.464 --> 39:04.049
- You're touching me!
- Not touching.

39:04.133 --> 39:06.760
- Touching me!
- It's free air.

